WEBVTT

00:02:00.402 --> 00:02:04.438
Ukweli ni kwamba jamii za kiraia,
waandishi wa habari na wanaharakati

00:02:04.462 --> 00:02:09.291
wanashambuliwa zaidi na makundi
yenye siasa kali kwa upande mmoja,

00:02:09.315 --> 00:02:11.045
na katika nchi nyingi,

00:02:11.069 --> 00:02:13.504
pia kutoka kwenye serikali zao wenyewe.

00:02:13.528 --> 00:02:16.920
Tunaona waandishi wa blogu
na waandishi wa habari wakifungwa,

00:02:16.944 --> 00:02:18.382
wakishtakiwa na kutishwa

00:02:18.406 --> 00:02:19.924
na serikali zao wenyewe,

00:02:19.948 --> 00:02:23.343
wengi ambao wanashirikiana na nchi
za Magharibi katika vita vya ugaidi

00:02:23.785 --> 00:02:25.422
Nitatoa mifano mitatu.

00:02:25.446 --> 00:02:27.302
Rafiki yangu na mshirika wangu zamani,

00:02:27.326 --> 00:02:28.558
Hisham Almiraat,

00:02:28.582 --> 00:02:31.626
ameshtakiwa kwa kutishia
usalama wa taifa,